{"tid":1841721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完政府記者會=要你班香港人陪葬","createTime":"2020-01-25T11:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:46:38.000Z","uid":237645,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7598118f97582a1a8b6ad8b2e23cac3f8c2879e9","tid":1841721,"uid":237645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驟眼睇好似做咗好多野 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">實際係頭4點係廢既</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">特首林鄭月娥宣布一系列抗疫措施，包括：<br />\n．無限期暫停來往武漢的航班及高鐵；<br />\n．擴大健康申報至所有口岸；<br />\n．加強口岸的體溫檢測並加強人手；<br />\n．呼籲市民切勿前往湖北省；<br />\n．取消大型活動如元宵晚會及渣打馬拉松；<br />\n．中小學、幼稚園及特殊學校延遲至2月17日復課</span><br />\n<br />\n要知道呢個政府 咩都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇數據</span></span><br />\n即係話要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死咗人</span></span> 先會覺得武漢肺炎好嚴重<br />\n到時先開始研究下一步點做 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我地要既五大訴求係</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消 港珠澳免費通行<br />\n封關<br />\n增加對前線醫護撥款<br />\n管制對藥房買醫療用品價錢<br />\n承諾為港人分發醫療物資</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府預真&middot;攬炒 <br />\n2003 教訓好沉重 多得政府隱瞞 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2020 全民口罩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人一個都不能少<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"261a152eb057abff9b55fba6e6d247967ec90b09","tid":1841721,"uid":237645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f3e8d9f9c2cb0146863aa79ec43c63a9b5648dd","tid":1841721,"uid":237645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f32bd291b9e3c96af9e6ef270e36cee3df2ea8df","tid":1841721,"uid":237645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"8d8a29e9c6dd4f0fc163214f19387a3fe07240e3","tid":18